* does
	* reads in Nigeria, WAVE 2 (2012-2013), POST HARVEST, AG SECTA2
	* determines harvest labor (only) for preceeding rainy season
	* outputs clean data file ready for combination with wave 2 plot data

* assumes
	* customsave.ado
	* mdesc.ado
	
